\c 43 Vanhu vanoenda Ijipiti vachitora naJeremiyawo 1 Zvino Jeremiya wakati apedza 4 kuudza vanhu mashoko ose aJehovha Mwari wavo, aakanga atumwa nawo kwavari naJehovha Mwari wavo, iwo mashoko awa ose, 2 ipapo Azaria mwanakomana waHoshaia, naJohanani mwanakomana waKarea, navarume vose, vaizvikudza, vakataura vachiti, kuna Jeremiya, "Unoreva nhema, Jehovha Mwari wedu haana kukutuma kuzoti, `Musaenda Ijipiti kundogarapo rnuri vatorwa; 3 asi Bharuki mwanakomana waNeria ndiye unokumutsa pamusoro pedu, kuti tiiswe mumaoko avaKaradhea, kuti vatiuraye nokutitapira Bhabhironi.' " 4 Naizvozvo Johanani mwanakomana waKarea, navakuru vose vehondo, navanhu vose, havana kuterera inzwi raJehovha, kuti vagare munyika yaJudha. 5 Asi Johanani mwanakomana waKarea, navakuru vose vehondo, vakatora vose vakasara vaJudha, vakanga vadzoka kumarudzi ose kwavakadzingirwa, vachida kugara vari vatorwa munyika yaJudha, 6 vaiti, varume navakadzi navana navakunda vamambo nomunhu upi noupi akanga asiyiwa naNebhuzaradhani mukuru wavarindi kuna Gedharia mwanakomana waAhikami, mwanakomana waShafani, pamwechete naJeremiya muporofita, naBharuki mwanakomana waNeria, 7 vakandosvika kunyika yeIjipiti; nokuti havana kuterera inzwi raJehovha; vakandosvika Tapanesi. 8 Ipapo shoko raJehovha rakasvika kuna Jeremiya paTapanesi, richiti, 9 "Tora mabwe makuru muruoko rwako, uavige muvhu pakati pezvitina, pavanopinda napo paimba yaFarao naTapanesi, vanhu vose vaJudha vachizviona; lOugoti kwavari, `Zvanzi naJehovha wehondo, mwari walsiraeri, Tarirai, ndichatuma shoko kundotora Nebhukadhirezari mambo weBhabhironi, muranda wangu, ndiise chigaro chake choushe pamusoro pamabwe awa andakaviga; uchawirira pamusoro pawo jira rake rinobwinya. 11 Uchauya achirova nyika yeIjipiti; vakafanira rufu vachaiswa kurufu, vakafanira kutapwa vachaiswa kukutapwa, vakafanira munondo vachaiswa kumunondo. 12Ndichabatidza moto mudzimba dzavamwari
